### How to develop locally.

{%- block LocalDevelopment %}
All the main commands to interact with the codebase are stored in the `Taskfile.yml` file. You can get
an exhaustive list of all the available commands by running `task help` in your terminal.

```shell
❯ task help
task: [help] task --list-all
task: Available tasks for this project:
* help:                           List all the tasks.
...
```

Here are the main commands you will need to use to develop locally:

* To list all the available tasks:

```shell
task help
```

* To install your local development environment:

```shell
task setup
```


